workflow_runs.display_title: Add CORS, improve posts API, and enhance frontend error handling

head_commit.message:
Add CORS, improve posts API, and enhance frontend error handling

Added CORS middleware to the FastAPI backend for cross-origin requests. Refactored the /api/posts endpoint to return a summary view and introduced /api/posts/full for posts with replies. Updated frontend JavaScript to use the new endpoint, improved error handling and validation, and fixed reply creation to use the correct API route.
